               <p>Last Tuesday three weeks I lost a sattin cloak out of my room where I lodge; it was hanging in a chair by the door; I saw the prisoner take it off the chair; I ran after her to stop her; but having my cap off she got away; I never saw my cloak again; 
               <persName id="t17790707-25-person252">
