                     <interp inst="t17790707-25-person253" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>The prisoner came to my room (Daniel lodged with me) to ask me to wash some things for her; I left the prisoner and Daniel in the room, while I went for a pint of beer. When I came back, Daniel was crying, Stop, thief! she said the prisoner had run away with her cloak off the chair. I went after her, but could not take her; I knew her very well.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I know nothing of the cloak.</p>
